I don't even know what I'm saying.

288
00:23:57,440 --> 00:23:59,840
Just pretend you didn't hear anything.

289
00:24:02,560 --> 00:24:04,840
The way he was rambling and shy,

290
00:24:06,240 --> 00:24:08,560
is a scene I would often dream of later on.

291
00:24:12,600 --> 00:24:18,160
Alright, for your homework, please write a 3
paragraph essay using any argument of your choice.

292
00:24:18,760 --> 00:24:20,520
It is due next monday.

293
00:24:20,880 --> 00:24:22,280
See you guys next week.

294
00:24:23,400 --> 00:24:24,400
Teacher, wait a moment!

295
00:24:26,200 --> 00:24:27,680
Three, two, one!

296
00:24:27,960 --> 00:24:32,120
Congradulations on your wedding, Teacher!

297
00:24:33,360 --> 00:24:34,440
Thank you..

298
00:24:40,040 --> 00:24:41,840
Now, please welcome the couple.

299
00:24:45,680 --> 00:24:46,680
Mr. Lu Feng,

300
00:24:46,720 --> 00:24:48,640
do you take Mr. Cheng
Yichen to be your husband?

301
00:24:50,200 --> 00:24:51,200
I do.

302
00:24:52,160 --> 00:24:53,160
Mr. Cheng Yichen,

303
00:24:53,320 --> 00:24:55,040
do you take Mr. Lu Feng to be your husband?

304
00:24:55,160 --> 00:24:56,160
I do.

305
00:25:01,600 --> 00:25:04,080
Now, please exchange rings.

306
00:25:21,080 --> 00:25:23,160
Knowing there won't
be a wedding of our own,

307
00:25:24,120 --> 00:25:25,120
right now,

308
00:25:26,120 --> 00:25:28,480
I'm just stealing a little bit of
someone else's happiness.

309
00:26:02,800 --> 00:26:04,560
I have something for you.

310
00:26:05,560 --> 00:26:06,800
I don't know if you'll like it.

311
00:26:06,880 --> 00:26:07,880
What is it?

312
00:26:12,640 --> 00:26:14,440
You're holding it so
tight, how can I see it?

313
00:26:25,800 --> 00:26:26,880
It's just silver.

314
00:26:27,160 --> 00:26:28,520
Nothing expensive.

315
00:26:30,640 --> 00:26:31,640
This...

316
00:26:31,720 --> 00:26:32,720
This one is yours.

317
00:26:37,680 --> 00:26:39,320
Do you not like it?

318
00:26:41,480 --> 00:26:42,600
I made it myself.

319
00:26:43,000 --> 00:26:44,600
It might be a bit rough.

320
00:26:49,800 --> 00:26:50,800
What's wrong?

321
00:26:51,400 --> 00:26:52,400
You...

322
00:26:52,840 --> 00:26:54,080
You don't like it that much?

323
00:26:56,840 --> 00:26:57,840
Lu Feng,

324
00:27:01,560 --> 00:27:02,560
I love you.

325
00:27:11,160 --> 00:27:12,200
I love you too.

326
00:27:19,520 --> 00:27:20,520
Look.

327
00:27:20,960 --> 00:27:23,040
Lu Feng loves Cheng Yichen.

328
00:27:45,040 --> 00:27:46,040
Lu Feng,

329
00:27:47,760 --> 00:27:49,440
can you promise me something?

330
00:27:51,400 --> 00:27:53,760
If we ever break up one day,

331
00:27:54,840 --> 00:27:55,840
the ring...

332
00:27:56,720 --> 00:27:57,760
don't take it back.

333
00:27:59,320 --> 00:28:00,640
I can pay for it.

334
00:28:01,720 --> 00:28:02,720
Just leave it with me.

335
00:28:03,080 --> 00:28:04,080
Okay?

336
00:28:11,160 --> 00:28:12,680
We will never break up.

337
00:28:15,040 --> 00:28:16,880
I want to be with you
for the rest of my life.

338
00:28:25,360 --> 00:28:27,680
A kiss as sincere and tangible as this,

339
00:28:28,720 --> 00:28:29,720
in the future,

340
00:28:30,240 --> 00:28:31,920
no one else will ever be able to give me.

341
00:28:32,800 --> 00:28:33,800
This isn't...

342
00:28:35,440 --> 00:28:36,440
This...

343
00:28:37,920 --> 00:28:38,920
They...

344
00:28:39,560 --> 00:28:40,560
Damn it.

345
00:28:46,200 --> 00:28:48,000
I personally respect

346
00:28:48,120 --> 00:28:49,240
your freedom to love,

347
00:28:50,320 --> 00:28:51,400
but the impact

348
00:28:52,320 --> 00:28:53,320
is very negative.

349
00:28:53,760 --> 00:28:54,760
I brought you here today

350
00:28:54,960 --> 00:28:56,280
to clarify that

351
00:28:56,520 --> 00:28:58,280
you're just messing around.

352
00:28:58,440 --> 00:28:59,440
Messing around?

353
00:29:00,040 --> 00:29:02,080
Principal, you're the one messing around.

354
00:29:02,520 --> 00:29:04,120
We are in a serious relationship.

355
00:29:04,240 --> 00:29:05,600
Two men in a relationship?

356
00:29:05,760 --> 00:29:07,520
Who says two men
can't be in a relationship?

357
00:29:07,960 --> 00:29:09,240
Is there a law against it?

358
00:29:10,040 --> 00:29:11,200
We haven't broken any laws,

359
00:29:11,360 --> 00:29:12,720
nor have we violated school rules.

360
00:29:12,840 --> 00:29:14,440
Does us being together bother you?

361
00:29:15,120 --> 00:29:16,840
Your family pays for your college education

362
00:29:17,080 --> 00:29:18,440
for you to do this?

363
00:29:19,120 --> 00:29:20,120
He's innocent.

364
00:29:20,320 --> 00:29:21,640
He was forced by me.

365
00:29:22,520 --> 00:29:24,120
The school can't handle you two anymore.

366
00:29:24,320 --> 00:29:25,600
I suggest you transfer schools.

367
00:29:27,840 --> 00:29:30,400
His desperate
struggle to protect me

368
00:29:31,440 --> 00:29:33,240
made me feel bad for him.

369
00:29:37,040 --> 00:29:38,560
I won't let you be transferred.

370
00:29:39,200 --> 00:29:40,200
I'll leave instead.

371
00:29:40,760 --> 00:29:42,520
And then I'll sneak back to see you.

372
00:29:43,360 --> 00:29:45,240
But my parents must already know.

373
00:29:46,680 --> 00:29:47,800
Let them know.

374
00:29:48,320 --> 00:29:49,320
If they ask you,

375
00:29:49,360 --> 00:29:50,760
just say I forced you.

376
00:29:51,520 --> 00:29:53,160
Your dad must know too.

377
00:29:53,320 --> 00:29:54,440
I'm not afraid of him.

378
00:29:55,240 --> 00:29:57,080
The worst he can do is beat me.

379
00:29:57,520 --> 00:29:58,720
As long as he doesn't kill me,

380
00:29:59,040 --> 00:30:00,320
I will definitely be with you.

381
00:30:02,840 --> 00:30:03,960
Isn't that Lu Feng?

382
00:30:04,640 --> 00:30:06,120
Holding hands with a man?

383
00:30:06,800 --> 00:30:07,840
Aren't you disgusted?

384
00:30:07,960 --> 00:30:09,240
You're the disgusting one.

385
00:30:09,680 --> 00:30:10,840
What the hell are you?

386
00:30:11,000 --> 00:30:12,120
Why are you everywhere?

387
00:30:13,200 --> 00:30:14,840
We're in a legitimate relationship.

388
00:30:15,320 --> 00:30:16,160
What's it to you?

389
00:30:16,240 --> 00:30:17,320
Lu Feng, let's go.

390
00:30:17,640 --> 00:30:18,760
Lu Feng, is he fun?

391
00:30:20,560 --> 00:30:21,640
Who told you to touch him?

392
00:30:22,320 --> 00:30:23,000
Are you okay?

393
00:30:23,120 --> 00:30:24,120
I'm fine.

394
00:30:27,280 --> 00:30:28,296
Alright, alright, alright.

395
00:30:28,320 --> 00:30:29,320
You've got guts.

396
00:30:29,440 --> 00:30:30,576
You guys, all of you, attack!

397
00:30:30,600 --> 00:30:31,600
Beat him to death!

398
00:30:32,080 --> 00:30:33,576
What are you doing? What are you doing?

399
00:30:33,600 --> 00:30:34,600
Come here.

400
00:30:34,640 --> 00:30:35,840
Let me have some fun with you.

401
00:30:35,920 --> 00:30:37,039
Get lost! Bullshit!

402
00:30:37,040 --> 00:30:38,320
Still talking back? Let go!

403
00:30:38,440 --> 00:30:39,559
Let go! If Lu Feng can have
fun with him, why can't I?

404
00:30:39,560 --> 00:30:42,040
I'll strip you naked and see
if you're still so tough. Let go!

405
00:30:43,040 --> 00:30:44,040
Let go.

406
00:30:44,360 --> 00:30:45,400
Get the hell away from me!

407
00:30:48,080 --> 00:30:49,080
Lu Feng!

408
00:30:52,320 --> 00:30:53,320
Get lost!

409
00:30:56,560 --> 00:30:57,560
Let go!

410
00:30:58,840 --> 00:31:00,280
Who told you to touch him, Lu Feng?

411
00:31:00,880 --> 00:31:02,000
Looking back,

412
00:31:03,040 --> 00:31:04,720
I must have been out of my mind with fear,

413
00:31:05,360 --> 00:31:07,760
to have screamed so
desperately for Lu Feng to save me.

414
00:31:08,600 --> 00:31:10,080
Touch him again and see what happens!

415
00:31:15,200 --> 00:31:16,200
Lu Feng!

416
00:31:16,360 --> 00:31:17,360
Are you okay?

417
00:31:18,720 --> 00:31:19,720
Are you alright?

418
00:31:33,120 --> 00:31:33,760
Get inside!

419
00:31:33,920 --> 00:31:34,440
Dad!

420
00:31:34,720 --> 00:31:35,160
Dad!

421
00:31:35,160 --> 00:31:36,160
Stop causing us trouble!

422
00:31:36,160 --> 00:31:37,160
Dad! Mom!

423
00:31:37,161 --> 00:31:38,920
- Get inside!
- Dad, please, let me out!

424
00:31:39,080 --> 00:31:41,680
Dad! Dad! Dad!

425
00:31:44,000 --> 00:31:45,320
He just made a mistake, Mom!

426
00:31:45,440 --> 00:31:46,976
We can't let him keep
making these mistakes.

427
00:31:47,000 --> 00:31:49,199
Dad! Dad! Dad!

428
00:31:49,200 --> 00:31:50,080
Don't call me Dad.

429
00:31:50,160 --> 00:31:51,400
I never raised a son like you.

430
00:31:51,640 --> 00:31:53,400
Stay in there and think long and hard.

431
00:31:53,560 --> 00:31:54,480
When you've finally come to your senses,

432
00:31:54,520 --> 00:31:55,800
that's when I'll let you out.

433
00:31:56,200 --> 00:31:58,600
Xiao Chen, just listen
to your father this time.

434
00:31:58,680 --> 00:31:59,896
You can't keep acting like this.

435
00:31:59,920 --> 00:32:01,216
Do you have any idea how serious this is?

436
00:32:01,240 --> 00:32:03,160
You've already been expelled!

437
00:32:03,480 --> 00:32:04,920
You can't keep being so reckless.

438
00:32:08,080 --> 00:32:09,960
Mom, please, let me out!

439
00:32:10,040 --> 00:32:11,480
- I'm begging you, Mom!
- No.

440
00:32:11,640 --> 00:32:14,040
Begging won't help. Just
reflect on what you've done.

441
00:32:14,120 --> 00:32:15,120
Mom!

442
00:32:25,840 --> 00:32:26,840
Let me ask you something.

443
00:32:27,080 --> 00:32:28,160
You're involved with a man.

444
00:32:28,240 --> 00:32:29,400
Do you realize you're wrong?

445
00:32:29,680 --> 00:32:30,680
I'm not wrong.

446
00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:33,280
I just love him.

447
00:32:38,720 --> 00:32:39,720
Today...

448
00:32:40,160 --> 00:32:41,440
I'm going to beat you to death!

449
00:32:41,880 --> 00:32:42,880
Dad!

450
00:32:44,320 --> 00:32:45,440
Everything is taken care of.

451
00:32:45,640 --> 00:32:47,160
They've agreed to settle out of court.

452
00:32:47,440 --> 00:32:49,480
I'll have the finance
department prepare the money.

453
00:32:49,800 --> 00:32:51,320
And the plane ticket is booked.

454
00:32:53,440 --> 00:32:54,080
A plane ticket?

455
00:32:54,400 --> 00:32:55,840
Sis, what plane ticket?

456
00:32:56,240 --> 00:32:57,240
Keep your voice down.

457
00:32:58,320 --> 00:32:59,320
Where are you sending me?

458
00:32:59,640 --> 00:33:00,640
The day after tomorrow.

459
00:33:01,360 --> 00:33:02,520
Take him and leave first.

460
00:33:03,520 --> 00:33:04,840
I'll handle the Yang family.

461
00:33:05,520 --> 00:33:06,520
My money...

462
00:33:06,800 --> 00:33:08,080
isn't so easy to take.

463
00:33:12,720 --> 00:33:13,960
Sis, what plane ticket?

464
00:33:14,120 --> 00:33:15,000
Are you sending me to the States?

465
00:33:15,120 --> 00:33:15,960
I need to find Xiao Chen!

466
00:33:16,040 --> 00:33:16,840
I don't want to go to the States!

467
00:33:16,920 --> 00:33:18,016
- Sis, I don't want to go to the States!
- Stop shouting!

468
00:33:18,040 --> 00:33:19,216
- I don't want to go!
- Stop it!

469
00:33:19,240 --> 00:33:20,760
Aren't you afraid Dad will kill you?

470
00:33:21,520 --> 00:33:22,760
Just be obedient for now, okay?

471
00:33:22,920 --> 00:33:25,080
You'll have other chances
once you're in the States.

472
00:33:26,400 --> 00:33:27,600
Don't be so anxious right now.

473
00:33:27,880 --> 00:33:30,080
Aren't you afraid of what Dad
might do to Cheng Yichen?

474
00:33:35,000 --> 00:33:36,000
Sis.

475
00:33:36,840 --> 00:33:37,840
Do me a favor.

476
00:33:39,440 --> 00:33:41,440
Please, send a message to Xiao Chen for me.

477
00:33:42,200 --> 00:33:43,000
Tell him...

478
00:33:43,200 --> 00:33:44,840
that I will definitely come back for him.

479
00:33:45,320 --> 00:33:46,960
I'm only going to the States for a while.

480
00:33:47,160 --> 00:33:48,440
Will you do this for me?

481
00:34:01,040 --> 00:34:02,040
Xiao Chen,

482
00:34:02,120 --> 00:34:04,376
my family has already handled
the situation with Yang Wei.

483
00:34:04,400 --> 00:34:05,400
Don't worry.

484
00:34:05,560 --> 00:34:07,056
I'm flying to the States
the day after tomorrow.

485
00:34:07,080 --> 00:34:08,640
My dad wants me to lay low for a while.

486
00:34:08,680 --> 00:34:10,080
But I'll be back soon.

487
00:34:10,280 --> 00:34:11,480
You must wait for me.

488
00:34:30,520 --> 00:34:31,520
Sis.

489
00:34:33,000 --> 00:34:34,000
Go on.

490
00:35:02,440 --> 00:35:03,440
Brother.

491
00:35:04,280 --> 00:35:05,440
Mom and Dad are still asleep.

492
00:35:05,960 --> 00:35:07,080
Have something to eat, okay?

493
00:35:07,280 --> 00:35:08,280
Cheng Yi-chen.

494
00:35:09,400 --> 00:35:10,400
Cheng Yi-chen.

495
00:35:11,560 --> 00:35:12,880
Please, let me out.

496
00:35:14,840 --> 00:35:15,840
Brother.

497
00:35:17,200 --> 00:35:18,816
How much longer are you
going to be this stubborn?

498
00:35:18,840 --> 00:35:20,296
I don't know or care about
anything else right now.

499
00:35:20,320 --> 00:35:21,680
I just want to see him.

500
00:35:22,440 --> 00:35:23,840
Just let me see him one last time.

501
00:35:24,200 --> 00:35:25,200
See who?

502
00:35:25,600 --> 00:35:26,600
That freak?

503
00:35:26,840 --> 00:35:28,160
He's ruined you
into such a state!

504
00:35:29,320 --> 00:35:31,120
But you don't have to
think about it anymore.

505
00:35:32,680 --> 00:35:34,000
He's leaving for the States soon.

506
00:35:36,713 --> 00:35:37,913
He's never coming back.

507
00:35:46,400 --> 00:35:47,520
How do you know?

508
00:35:49,040 --> 00:35:50,040
That's impossible.

509
00:35:50,240 --> 00:35:51,240
Why is it impossible?

510
00:35:51,320 --> 00:35:52,120
His family is so well-known.

511
00:35:52,240 --> 00:35:53,600
It's easy to find out.

512
00:35:54,000 --> 00:35:55,920
He's being charged with attempted murder.

513
00:35:56,080 --> 00:35:57,399
The only reason he's
not in jail is because...

514
00:35:57,400 --> 00:35:58,840
his family has so much influence.

515
00:36:00,120 --> 00:36:01,760
Their business is already in the States.

516
00:36:02,280 --> 00:36:03,280
Sending him abroad...

517
00:36:03,800 --> 00:36:05,000
is just the logical next step.

518
00:36:06,200 --> 00:36:07,920
No, that can't be. I have to find him!

519
00:36:08,280 --> 00:36:09,280
Brother!

520
00:36:09,800 --> 00:36:10,800
Brother, I'm begging you!

521
00:36:11,440 --> 00:36:12,440
Please, don't go!

522
00:36:13,120 --> 00:36:14,120
Don't go!

523
00:36:16,207 --> 00:36:18,447
It's for the best that he's leaving.

524
00:36:18,902 --> 00:36:21,240
Once he's gone, you can go
back to being normal, right?

525
00:36:21,393 --> 00:36:22,393
Right?

526
00:36:22,680 --> 00:36:23,680
We are normal people.

527
00:36:23,681 --> 00:36:24,799
Our feelings are normal.

528
00:36:24,800 --> 00:36:26,040
We haven't done anything wrong.

529
00:36:26,760 --> 00:36:27,760
Brother!

530
00:36:29,560 --> 00:36:30,960
Don't force me to call Mom and Dad.

531
00:36:32,880 --> 00:36:33,880
Cheng Yi-chen.

532
00:36:34,160 --> 00:36:35,160
I'm begging you.

533
00:36:36,120 --> 00:36:37,440
Just let me see him once.

534
00:36:38,000 --> 00:36:39,000
Can I?

535
00:36:41,200 --> 00:36:43,000
This is the only hope I have left.

536
00:36:43,880 --> 00:36:45,520
I can't give up on it.

537
00:36:50,760 --> 00:36:51,760
Please?

538
00:36:53,040 --> 00:36:54,400
Just let me see him once.

539
00:36:55,240 --> 00:36:56,240
Please?

540
00:36:59,640 --> 00:37:01,080
What good will it do if you go?

541
00:37:02,640 --> 00:37:03,960
He's still going to leave anyway.

542
00:37:04,560 --> 00:37:05,560
He promised me...

543
00:37:06,800 --> 00:37:08,600
that we would be together forever.

544
00:37:09,320 --> 00:37:10,120
I just want to ask him...

545
00:37:10,121 --> 00:37:11,680
if that promise still holds true.

546
00:37:12,080 --> 00:37:13,080
Cheng Yi-chen.

547
00:37:13,400 --> 00:37:14,400
Don't worry.

548
00:37:14,800 --> 00:37:15,920
I won't stop him.

549
00:37:16,400 --> 00:37:17,680
I just want an answer.

550
00:37:23,960 --> 00:37:24,960
I'm done with you!

551
00:37:33,000 --> 00:37:34,000
Let go!

552
00:37:34,960 --> 00:37:35,640
Let go!

553
00:37:35,880 --> 00:37:36,880
Let go!

554
00:37:38,920 --> 00:37:39,920
Sis!

555
00:37:41,760 --> 00:37:42,760
Sis!

556
00:37:45,880 --> 00:37:46,880
Sis!

557
00:37:48,000 --> 00:37:49,000
Young Master.

558
00:37:49,200 --> 00:37:50,200
Get in the car.

559
00:37:53,320 --> 00:37:54,320
Sis!

560
00:37:54,920 --> 00:37:57,400
Sis! Sis! Sis!

561
00:37:59,120 --> 00:38:01,680
Sis, I can't leave yet!

562
00:38:02,680 --> 00:38:04,520
- I don't know about Xiao Chen...
- Lu Feng!

563
00:38:05,720 --> 00:38:06,680
If you keep acting like this,

564
00:38:06,681 --> 00:38:08,201
there's nothing more I can do for you.

565
00:38:26,200 --> 00:38:27,640
Stop the car! Driver, stop the car!

566
00:38:31,360 --> 00:38:32,360
Lu Feng!

567
00:38:32,600 --> 00:38:33,600
Lu Feng!

568
00:38:34,800 --> 00:38:35,800
Brother!

569
00:38:38,080 --> 00:38:39,080
Lu Feng!

570
00:38:41,880 --> 00:38:42,920
Lu Feng!

571
00:38:45,480 --> 00:38:46,560
Lu Feng!

572
00:38:49,480 --> 00:38:50,800
Lu Feng!

573
00:38:52,360 --> 00:38:53,800
Lu Feng!

574
00:39:01,280 --> 00:39:02,320
Lu Feng!

575
00:39:04,120 --> 00:39:05,120
Lu Feng!

576
00:39:05,360 --> 00:39:06,360
Brother!

577
00:39:06,400 --> 00:39:07,400
Lu Feng!

578
00:39:08,800 --> 00:39:09,800
Lu Feng!

579
00:39:10,520 --> 00:39:11,120
Brother!

580
00:39:11,120 --> 00:39:12,120
Lu Feng!

581
00:39:12,360 --> 00:39:13,360
Brother!

582
00:39:13,840 --> 00:39:14,840
Lu Feng!

583
00:39:15,920 --> 00:39:16,920
Let's go home.

584
00:39:21,640 --> 00:39:22,920
Cheng Yi-chen was right.

585
00:39:24,400 --> 00:39:25,840
It really was too late.

586
00:39:29,880 --> 00:39:31,000
Lu Feng!

587
00:39:37,960 --> 00:39:38,960
Cheng Yichen!

588
00:39:58,040 --> 00:39:59,040
Brother!

589
00:39:59,760 --> 00:40:00,760
I'll see you off.

590
00:40:08,080 --> 00:40:09,240
After this incident,

591
00:40:10,440 --> 00:40:12,240
I transferred schools just like Lu Feng.

592
00:40:13,600 --> 00:40:15,840
Everyone pretended
that nothing had happened.

593
00:40:17,640 --> 00:40:20,160
I knew something had slipped away from me,

594
00:40:21,720 --> 00:40:23,400
but I couldn't put it into words.

595
00:40:30,640 --> 00:40:32,240
Call me when you get to your new school.

596
00:41:26,440 --> 00:41:28,280
How much longer are
you going to keep this up?

597
00:41:44,240 --> 00:41:45,880
Where is my passport?

598
00:41:46,720 --> 00:41:47,720
Stop asking.

599
00:41:48,033 --> 00:41:50,033
Even if you had it, you
wouldn't be able to leave.

600
00:41:51,040 --> 00:41:52,376
Give me back my passport right now!

601
00:41:52,400 --> 00:41:53,920
I have to go back to see Cheng Yichen!

602
00:41:55,320 --> 00:41:56,320
You want to see him?

603
00:41:56,480 --> 00:41:58,000
Do you think he even wants to see you?

604
00:41:59,480 --> 00:42:00,520
Has he reached out to you?

605
00:42:00,600 --> 00:42:02,040
Has he ever written you back?

606
00:42:02,960 --> 00:42:03,680
Have you ever considered

607
00:42:03,681 --> 00:42:05,840
that he might have moved
on and started a new life?

608
00:42:06,400 --> 00:42:08,160
Do you think everyone is as foolish as you?

609
00:42:09,640 --> 00:42:11,376
To give up your
education and your family

610
00:42:11,400 --> 00:42:13,336
for a relationship that
has to stay in the shadows?

611
00:42:13,360 --> 00:42:15,000
You gave up everything you had.

612
00:42:16,680 --> 00:42:18,160
Just look at yourself now.

613
00:42:18,600 --> 00:42:20,120
Is this even what a person looks like?

614
00:42:50,049 --> 00:42:52,537
(Four years later)

615
00:43:03,640 --> 00:43:04,640
When this is over,

616
00:43:04,800 --> 00:43:06,240
aren't you going to buy him a drink?

617
00:43:06,960 --> 00:43:08,039
He's still just a kid.

618
00:43:08,040 --> 00:43:09,040
Why would he be drinking?

619
00:43:13,920 --> 00:43:14,760
It's been so long.

620
00:43:14,920 --> 00:43:16,160
Still no progress?
